title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data from table inside a grid cell
OB: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table that is inside a grid cell.
EB: No exception should be thrown when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell.
SR: To reproduce the issue:  1. Insert a grid.  2. Insert a table into one of the grid cells.  3. Insert another table into another grid cell.
